<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 06:18:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>早盘竞价：亚洲因鸽派利率希望而反弹</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-29/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>四国外长谴责南中国海的危险行动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-tokyo-talks-maritime-security-cyber-2024-07-29/</link><description>澳大利亚、印度、日本和美国外长周一表示，他们对南中国海的恐吓和危险行为感到严重关切，并承诺加强该地区的海上安全。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:18:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/quad-foreign-ministers-meet-tokyo-talks-maritime-security-cyber-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>法院称碧桂园清算听证会推迟至明年一月</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-january-next-year-court-says-2024-07-29/</link><description>香港一家法院周一将寻求碧桂园清算请愿书的听证会推迟至 2025 年 1 月 20 日，这让这家陷入困境的中国开发商有了喘息的机会，该开发商正试图敲定离岸债务重组计划。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 02:16:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/country-garden-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-january-next-year-court-says-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>债权人寻求破产程序后，中国恒大的电动汽车部门下线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-china-evergrande-new-energy-vehicle-set-open-up-9-2024-07-29/</link><description>周一早盘，中国恒大新能源汽车股价下跌 7%，此前该公司旗下两家子公司的个人债权人寻求法院批准这些子公司进入破产程序并进行重组。</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 01:41:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/shares-china-evergrande-new-energy-vehicle-set-open-up-9-2024-07-29/</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜金正恩视察中国边境附近的洪水地区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-inspects-flooded-areas-near-china-border-kcna-says-2024-07-28/</link><description>金正恩指责官员们对危机应对措施的准备不足。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 22:45:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-jong-un-inspects-flooded-areas-near-china-border-kcna-says-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>梅洛尼誓言“重启”意大利与中国的合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-vows-relaunch-cooperation-with-china-ansa-2024-07-28/</link><description>意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼周日誓言要“重启”与中国的合作，并在上任以来首次正式访问北京期间签署了一项三年行动计划。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 10:44:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/italys-meloni-vows-relaunch-cooperation-with-china-ansa-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称中国曲解南海协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-mischaracterised-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-deal-2024-07-28/</link><description>一名中国官员表示，中国海警在执行任务前接到通知，并在“现场确认”后放行了一艘船只。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 08:29:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-says-china-mischaracterised-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-deal-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>美国升级驻日军事指挥权，警告中国威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-announce-military-command-revamp-japan-official-says-2024-07-28/</link><description>美国周日宣布计划对其驻日军事指挥部进行重大调整，以加深与其盟友部队的协调，两国将中国视为该地区面临的“最大战略挑战”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 03:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/us-announce-military-command-revamp-japan-official-says-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜在朝鲜战争周年纪念日发誓“彻底消灭”敌人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-vows-total-destruction-enemy-korean-war-anniversary-2024-07-28/</link><description>据朝鲜官方媒体朝中社周日报道，朝鲜领导人金正恩下令，誓言一旦发生战争，将“彻底摧毁”敌人。</description><pubDate>Sun, 28 Jul 2024 00:36:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-vows-total-destruction-enemy-korean-war-anniversary-2024-07-28/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普誓言要建立比特币“储备”，并援引中国的竞争</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/trump-cites-china-competition-vowing-create-bitcoin-stockpile-2024-07-27/</link><description>共和党总统候选人唐纳德·特朗普在周六的比特币会议上表示，美国必须主导该行业，否则中国就会主导该行业，这是他向加密货币倡导者讨好的最新举措，北京已限制加密货币，他曾将其斥为“骗局”。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 23:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/trump-cites-china-competition-vowing-create-bitcoin-stockpile-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯与王讨论台湾和中国对俄罗斯的支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-conveys-concern-wang-over-provocative-actions-taiwan-us-official-says-2024-07-27/</link><description>美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周六会见中国外长王毅时，重申了华盛顿对北京对台湾行动的担忧以及对俄罗斯乌克兰战争的支持。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 11:37:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-conveys-concern-wang-over-provocative-actions-taiwan-us-official-says-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”迫使中国东北地区疏散、工厂停工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/typhoon-gaemi-forces-evacuation-factory-suspension-northeast-china-2024-07-27/</link><description>据官方新华社周六报道，由于台风“盖美”带来大雨，中国东北地区有超过 27,000 人被疏散，数百家工厂被勒令停产。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 09:25:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/typhoon-gaemi-forces-evacuation-factory-suspension-northeast-china-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾完成与北京达成协议以来首次南海补给任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-completes-first-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-since-deal-with-2024-07-27/</link><description>菲律宾外交部表示，周六，菲律宾在有争议的南海浅滩顺利完成了向其部队进行的补给行动，这是与中国达成的旨在缓和紧张局势的新安排下的首次此类任务。</description><pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 05:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-completes-first-south-china-sea-resupply-mission-since-deal-with-2024-07-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车电池制造商CATL第二季度利润增长更快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-posts-134-jump-second-quarter-profit-2024-07-26/</link><description>中国电动汽车电池巨头宁德时代第二季度利润增长更快，尽管全球最大汽车市场的电动汽车需求放缓，而地缘政治紧张局势给其海外扩张蒙上了阴影。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 11:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-posts-134-jump-second-quarter-profit-2024-07-26/</guid></item><item><title>投资者表示，税收漏洞的终结可能会削弱 Shein 的 IPO 吸引力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/end-tax-loophole-risks-dimming-sheins-ipo-appeal-investors-say-2024-07-26/</link><description>关注该行业的投资者表示，欧盟和其他地区当局终止低价值包裹税收减免的举措威胁到了 Shein 的盈利能力，并有可能削弱这家快时尚零售商在计划上市之前的长期吸引力。</description><pubDate>Fri, 26 Jul 2024 08:14:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/end-tax-loophole-risks-dimming-sheins-ipo-appeal-investors-say-2024-07-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>